========================================================================
===================            NOTES               =====================
========================================================================

* tools/feedme.py lets you fill scrib's brain with text from a file.
* There are some other in-dev tools that use PHP to feed scrib some
  naughtiness in a basket.

========================================================================
===================        WHAT YOU NEED           =====================
========================================================================

* python-irclib
	 ( http://python-irclib.sourceforge.net/ 
	   Most distros: install python-irclib			       )

* espeak (optional)
	(  http://espeak.sourceforge.net/
	   If you wish to use the voice-grue or voice-scrib, you'll
	   need to install espeak.
	   Most distros: install espeak				       )

* Will be moving to using PyBrain.

